Check object

Source: R/plot_support_function.R
check_object.Rd

Checks if the object is of desired class

check_object(object, type = "res")

Arguments

object

Object passed to the function
type

Type of check; default is res which stands for "model residuals". Other possible values: eva - model evaluation
